  1→// ── Chat page (Preact + JSX) ────────────────────────────────────────
  2→// This is a TypeScript/JSX conversion of page-chat.js. The page is
  3→// heavily imperative (DOM manipulation + registerPrefix router pattern)
  4→// so the conversion preserves that style while adding types.
  5→
  6→// NOTE: The chatPageHTML constant uses innerHTML assignment which is safe
  7→// because it is a compile-time static string with no user input interpolated.
  8→// The original JS file documents this explicitly. The eslint-disable comment
  9→// is preserved from the original source.
 10→
